author: Moira Macdonald
title: Sunday Best: The great Cate
text:
I’ve no idea what Cate Blanchett is reacting to in this shot, taken at a recent red-carpet event for her upcoming movie “Truth.” But I suspect she might have had a similar expression on her face upon first seeing this fairy-tale of a dress, from Schiaparelli. It’s black velvet, festooned with gloriously colorful embroidered and sequined flowers; an enchanted garden, in dress form.
